259
00:17:43,040 --> 00:17:44,155
- Bonjour.
- Bonjour.

260
00:17:44,240 --> 00:17:46,470
Enchantée. C'est pour vous.

261
00:17:47,200 --> 00:17:49,270
- Merci.
- De rien.

262
00:17:50,880 --> 00:17:52,359
